         I believe much like normal mobs pets have resting and fighting regeneration values.  So 7% while at rest is not that out of line, it is probably much, much lower when engaged in combat.</P><P>VI will not nerf the gloves, comparing them to the old CH BPs is silly.  These drop off one of the harder VT mobs and seem to be pretty rare (have not seen a set fall in about 6 slayings) and at best maybe .5% of Necromancers or Mages upon any given server will see them.</P><P>Have not seen any reports of the effect upon EoT yet.  Mages seem to think it caused a HP upgrade, so I am wondering how much EoT would gain.</P><P>Bril</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
